snippet.title: Solving Radical Equations
snippet.description:
Learn how to solve radical equations in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.  We go through 2 different examples.

0:19 How to Solve Radical Equations...Isolating the Radical
0:48 Squaring Both Sides
1:01 Checking for Extraneous Roots
1:52 Example 2 3x^(2/3) -2 = 10
2:01 Rewriting the Rational Exponent as a Radical
2:32 Raising Both Sides to the Reciprocal Power

Related Videos:

Solving More Challenging Radical Equations
